OL,3,CFuneral for WW2 veteran who touched
OL,4,Cthe hearts of thousands
OL,6,FJennifer Buck reports on the final
OL,7,Ftribute to a war hero in Preston.
OL,9,FThe funeral of one of the oldest
OL,10,Fsurviving World War Two veterans has
OL,11,Ftaken place in Preston.
OL,13,FErnest Horsfall died two months short
OL,14,Fof turning 106. Today he received a
OL,15,Ffull guard of honour at Fulwood Free
OL,16,FMethodist Church.
OL,18,FHe spoke to Granada Reports on his
OL,19,Flast birthday, when he received more
OL,20,Fthan four thousand cards.
