OL,6,FErnest Horsfall, was born in Bradford
OL,7,Fin 1918. He served with the Royal
OL,8,FElectrical and Mechanical Engineers as
OL,9,Fa staff sergeant from 1940 to 1946.
OL,10,FAfter the war he settled in Preston.
OL,12,FHe was married for 57 years and had a
OL,13,Fson and a sister, but no longer had
OL,14,Fany surviving family members or
OL,15,Ffriends.
OL,17,FAfter hearing his story, the Royal
OL,18,FBritish Legion started an appeal to
OL,19,Fcollect birthday cards for him - and
OL,20,Fthey were inundated.
