OL,6,FHe received thousands of cards -
OL,7,Fincluding one from the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fand the King, but Ernest said he
OL,9,Fwasn't not sure what all the fuss was
OL,10,Fabout.
OL,12,FHe said: "I'm surprised anyone is
OL,13,Ftaking any notice to tell you the
OL,14,Ftruth."
OL,16,FThe Royal Electrical and Mechanical
OL,17,FEngineers and The Royal British Legion
OL,18,Fhave led tributes to Mr Horsfall.
