OL,6,FMatthew Nutter, Parade Marshall,
OL,7,FPreston City, paid this tribute to the
OL,8,Fveteran:
OL,10,FChristine Parry, Branch Secretary of
OL,11,Fthe Blackpool Royal British Legion,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We will be turning out to
OL,13,FErnest's funeral as we did at his
OL,14,F105th birthday last year. He was a
OL,15,Fsignificant part of a dwindling band
OL,16,Fof brothers, and our World War Two
OL,17,Fgeneration should never be forgotten."
