OL,6,FColonel David Waters (Retd), President
OL,7,Fof the Central Lancashire Armed Forces
OL,8,FVeterans Association, said: "Ernest
OL,9,Fwas a remarkable man. It would be easy
OL,10,Fto say he was one of life's characters
OL,11,Fbut he was a product of what he'd
OL,12,Flived through at an impressionable age
OL,13,Fand it forged him into the unique
OL,14,Fperson he was - indefatigable! We are
OL,15,Fall proud to have known him."
